"disadvantages": "Adalimumab can cause side effects such as infections, allergic reactions, and liver damage. It may not be suitable for patients with certain conditions such as heart failure, tuberculosis, or multiple sclerosis. It may also be less effective in patients who have previously failed treatment with another anti-TNF agent."
}
]

